_sText:
Slightly smaller version of http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/46752


On smaller server the backs of the map could cause rounds to drag a little, so I took that out and made it so you can't hide there anymore. I'm keeping the other version up because big servers might like that one better.

Other changes:
-Fixed various issues with players getting stuck
-Fixed a rare bug in the joker card

Made by: SmOoth.nl
Inspiration:www.cardstacker.com (I do realise it looks nothing like what he makes)


Enjoy,

SmOoth.nl
